      <h2 class="h2">Who is behind the charter?</h2>
      <p>The Manchester Homelessness Partnership has grown from collaboration with people who have experienced homelessness, charities, community and faith organisations, the council, businesses and other interested partners.</p>

      <h2 class="h2">How can I get involved?</h2>
      <p>You can make a personal pledge to support the charter, or join an action group working on key areas of improvement.</p>

      <h2 class="h2">How can my company get involved?</h2>
      <p>The Manchester Homelessness Partnership welcomes Manchester involvement from businesses. If you would like to speak to someone about how your business can get involved, please email <a href="charter@streetsupport.net">charter@streetsupport.net</a></p>
